{"tid":1422448,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[過來人]小小意見俾大汗既夢遊男士","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:27:17.000Z","uid":27670,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13f53dd97a8d7d58d09e5c2adf2fb10bcf0c9f5b","tid":1422448,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到有巴打分享<br />\n以後發夢唔好再著鬆身褲唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有部分巴打表示大肶罅俾底褲刮到好痛<br />\n我幾年前都俾呢個問題困擾<br />\n原因係份工本身會出汗+以前有打開波<br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔先<br />\n以下只係個人組驗<br />\n未必對所有人適用<br />\n如果好嚴重既話記得搵醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 唔好因為災情唔嚴重而忽視呢個問題<br />\n如果keep住唔理既話有機會會變成股癬<br />\n圖就唔po了 有興趣google 睇下 有小小核突<br />\n<br />\n當時我俾呢個問題困擾接近半年<br />\n情況開始嚴重先搵方法解決<br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n唔好著三角/四角底褲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QT2jyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QT2jyZ.jpg&h=5ee129cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpkPJ0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpkPJ0F.jpg&h=3c6b6b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原因係緊身 入面唔通風令底褲邊邊位長期都乾唔到<br />\n尤其三角褲如果係已經用左一段時間<br />\n佢係邊位既線會霉左<br />\n更加容易刮到大肶罅 (sorry for 1999)<br />\n如果你係大汗既巴打<br />\n建議你著孖煙通<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSkL1OU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSkL1OU.jpg&h=a7a50cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通風 d汗散得快d 亦都唔會刮大肶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始會覺得9 fing fing 咁 著幾日就會習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n搽藥膏<br />\n如果你已經被呢個問題困擾<br />\n唔好唔理 要搽藥膏<br />\n當時我係舊登搵資料 有人介紹用樂膚舒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jn6rMg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjn6rMg4.jpg&h=f0da72a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(唔擔保每個都岩用 有疑問記得睇醫生 非醫學撚and非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我係用藥膏裝 噴霧未用過唔評論<br />\n搽左1星期左右效果開始顯著<br />\n2星期接近完全消失<br />\n不過就算睇唔到都要keep住搽<br />\n我果時每晚沖完涼就搽 持續一個月<br />\n基本上接近完全斷尾<br />\n咁多年就算大肶罅有小小痕 沖涼捽多幾下第二朝幾乎都會冇事<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n沖涼<br />\n雖祭睇落好on9<br />\n但身邊認識唔少人洗頭+沖涼都係10分鍾搞掂<br />\n要沖乾淨d 尤其大腿內側同腋下 要捽耐d<br />\n就算之後好返 沖涼唔夠乾淨都會復發<br />\n<br />\n重申<br />\n以上只係個人經驗<br />\n有疑問請向醫生查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位夢遊巴打袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf99be309b6ea95bb9df3a59222c85cc21151c5c","tid":1422448,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:19:46.000Z","msg":"推俾大汗巴打參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e48a473b2c05fd2de7a76cd79d74aa8f165de09","tid":1422448,"uid":256565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}